{"tid":122481,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"到底係真理太賤 定愛德太水皮","createTime":"2017-02-16T05:16:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-16T07:32:51.000Z","uid":40442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6da497ead66082c03d5444a3344c5774528ac1de","tid":122481,"uid":40442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T05:16:34.000Z","msg":"愛德個國家嘅鍊金術係由地下父親大人整嘅賢者之石推動，所以打父親大人嗰時愛德一班人先俾人封技。<br />\n<br />\n但係愛德又好，師父都好都有見過真理，俾埋過路費但都唔知自己啲鍊金術係流嘢？<br />\n當佢地俾得少，但艾爾俾埋自己肉體都一樣唔知點解自己俾人封技？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔通真理淨係教物質構成，連鍊金術原理都唔教咁陰濕？可唔可以告佢不良銷售？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01225188f11586dc5e997a3fdba88c24ab775776","tid":122481,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T05:18:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bf4306c11e7ad3b77fef2f883526480a475354ae","tid":122481,"uid":14065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T05:54:17.000Z","msg":"唔係用緊父親大人嘅力量<br />\n而係父親大人封咗佢哋同地殻之間嘅連繫<br />\n所以用唔到<br />\n<br />\n佢地一直都係用緊鍊金術<br />\n之不過未係完全發揮晒咁解<br />\n因為有啲父親大人嘅阻力（啲管道）<br />\n後期已經解放返<br />\n可以100%用返出嚟"},{"pid":"8054238e88f944214f99ca1951ceff61ac7cae56","tid":122481,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T06:17:50.000Z","msg":"樓主見過真理  失去左智慧"},{"pid":"4e607a37cb693e4e0c7c7a98e06b737c2e037ec9","tid":122481,"uid":738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T06:45:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主見過真理  失去左智慧</blockquote><br />\n追求智慧 所以比真理收返智慧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5b67c5b54ed42b17491e21f23761aebfafb905d","tid":122481,"uid":12518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T06:47:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"325ae7220f8d7fec2c4897413058f525fb5c7499","tid":122481,"uid":38318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T06:48:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockqu